name: ファラオ
description: 砂に吞まれた帝国、灼熱の太陽に照らされた大砂漠──かつてそこを支配していたのは、強大な力を持つファラオたちだった。

wikiSkinData.lore: Boy-king of the southern wastes, Amumu's mummified body still haunts the halls of his ancient tomb. His mournful sobbing can be heard over the brutal desert winds, luring in unwitting adventurers.

Immortal beast of the northern lands, Nasus wanders the expanse of the Great Desert in search of his once-green kingdom. He conjures vast sandstorms to cover his tracks, hiding his existence from the world.

skins.name: ファラオ ニダリー

wikiSkinData.lore: Worshiped as a god-queen of the Great Desert, Nidalee is the avatar of the glorious cat-god, Sypakaa. As war tears through the land, Nidalee will do whatever it takes to protect her city and her temple from those who would dare threaten them.
